---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions | EB-1A Green Card Coach" description="Read the Terms and Conditions for EB-1A Green Card Coach website usage.">

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container legal-inner">
      <h1 class="heading-1 legal-title">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <hr class="divider" />

      <div class="legal-content">

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">1. Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-body">By accessing <a href="https://www.eb1agreencardcoach.com" class="legal-link">https://www.eb1agreencardcoach.com</a>, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. You are responsible for compliance with applicable local laws. Disagreement with any terms prohibits site access. The materials contained in this Website are protected by copyright and trade mark law.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">2. Use License</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Permission grants temporary download of materials for personal, non-commercial viewing only. This license prohibits you from:</p>
          <ul class="legal-list">
            <li>Modifying or copying materials</li>
            <li>Using materials for commercial purposes or public display</li>
            <li>Attempting to reverse engineer any software</li>
            <li>Removing copyright or proprietary notations</li>
            <li>Transferring materials to others or mirroring on other servers</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-body">The company may terminate access upon violation. Your viewing rights end upon termination, and you must destroy downloaded materials in all formats.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">3. Disclaimer</h2>
          <p class="text-body">All the materials on Eb1agreencardcoach's Website are provided "as is". The company makes no warranties regarding accuracy or reliability of materials or linked sites.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">4. Limitations</h2>
          <p class="text-body">The company and suppliers won't be held accountable for damages arising from material use or inability to use the site, even with prior notification of potential damage. Some jurisdictions may not allow these limitation provisions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">5. Revisions and Errata</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Materials may contain errors. The company doesn't guarantee accuracy, completeness, or currency and may change content without notice or commitment to updates.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">6. Links</h2>
          <p class="text-body">The company hasn't reviewed all linked sites and isn't responsible for their contents. Link presence doesn't imply endorsement. Users access linked sites at their own risk.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">7. Site Terms of Use Modifications</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Eb1agreencardcoach may revise these Terms of Use for its Website at any time without prior notice. By using this website, you agree to be bound by the current version of these Terms and Conditions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">8. Your Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Please review our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="legal-link">Privacy Policy</a> which also governs your visit to our website.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 legal-heading">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-body">Any claims relating to EB-1A Green Card Coach's website shall be governed by the applicable laws without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-inner { max-width: 860px; }

  .legal-title { margin-bottom: var(--sp-4); }

  .legal-content {
    margin-top: var(--sp-10);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-8);
  }

  .legal-section { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--sp-4); }

  .legal-heading { color: var(--color-navy); }

  .legal-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: var(--sp-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .legal-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    color: var(--color-text-body);
    line-height: var(--lh-body);
  }

  .legal-link {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .legal-link:hover { color: var(--color-primary-dark); }
</style>
